---
/**
 * Archived Post Warning Component
 * 
 * Displays a warning banner for archived posts that are kept for historical purposes.
 * Matches the Jekyll archived post warning functionality.
 * Uses Tailwind CSS for styling.
 */
---

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200 border-l-4 border-l-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-800 dark:border-l-yellow-600 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 mb-6 shadow-sm" role="alert">
  <strong>❗ Heads up!</strong> This post is archived and here for historical purposes. It may no longer be accurate or reflect my views. Proceed at your own risk.
</div>
